  "remarks": "JSC “Experimental Design Bureau ‘Crystal’” is a military industry company. It manufactures automotive and aircraft components (including fuel pumps for aircraft fuel systems, automatic engine control systems, and alternator drives), including for aicraft systems used by the Russian military in its war of aggression against Ukraine, such as components of the Su and MiG aircraft.",
